SUMMARY:[CONFERENCE] Service Design Global Conference 2026 (SDGC26)
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20261028
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20261030
LOCATION:RheinMain Congress Center, Wiesbaden, Frankfurt RheinMain region (onsite and online)
DESCRIPTION:The Service Design Global Conference 2026 (SDGC26) takes place 28-30 October in the Frankfurt RheinMain region, both onsite and online. It aims to discover how service design drives innovation and transforms modern organizations. The theme 'Beyond Boundaries: Enabling Solutions That Shape Tomorrow' explores how organizations across public and private sectors and the communities they serve can move past today’s limits to shape more resilient, meaningful futures through service design. SDGC26 brings together pioneers and practitioners for breakthrough ideas, practical tools, and meaningful connections, engaging with leading voices and exploring cutting-edge approaches to propel organizations forward. Link: https://www.servicedesignglobalconference.com/
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:a145bf6f8fe0ddc5c8daaece479e6f79
SUMMARY:[CONFERENCE] Service Design Global Conference 2026
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20261028
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20261030
LOCATION:Wiesbaden, Germany (RheinMain CongressCenter)
DESCRIPTION:The Service Design Global Conference 2026 (SDGC26) will take place from 28-30 October 2026, gathering the international Service Design community both in-person in Wiesbaden, in the vibrant Frankfurt RheinMain region, and online for virtual attendees. The conference is organized in cooperation with the World Design Capital 2026. The 3-day format includes workshops on 28 October (requiring separate purchase) followed by two full days of inspiring conference talks, keynotes, and panels on 29-30 October. In-person attendees will meet at the state-of-the-art RheinMain CongressCenter (RMCC). Link: https://www.service-design-network.org/events/sdgc-2026-germany
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:6d1d884dc2cde9af420e29001b5507e9
SUMMARY:[CONFERENCE] Service Design Global Conference 2026
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20261028
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20261030
LOCATION:RheinMain Congress Center, Friedrich-Ebert-Allee 1, 65185 Wiesbaden, Germany
DESCRIPTION:The Service Design Global Conference 2026 (SDGC26) is being held from October 28-30, 2026, at the RheinMain Congress Center in Wiesbaden, Germany. Early Bird tickets are available until June 30, 2026, offering savings for both in-person and virtual attendees. In-person tickets grant access to the conference on October 29-30, with an optional add-on for a closing event. Virtual tickets provide online access for the same dates, including a special rate for students. Workshops scheduled for October 28 are not included in these ticket types. Link: https://www.servicedesignglobalconference.com/event-details/service-design-global-conference-2026
END:VEVENT
