DESCRIPTION:The Service Design Network has announced that registration for the Service Design Global Conference 2026 (SDGC26) is officially open. The event brings the international Service Design community to Germany, with in-person attendance in Wiesbaden, in the vibrant Frankfurt RheinMain region, and online for virtual attendees. It is organized in cooperation with the World Design Capital Frankfurt RheinMain 2026. Link: https://wdo.org/event/service-design-global-conference-2026/
