DESCRIPTION:The prompt:UX Conference focuses on the intersection of artificial intelligence and user experience design, gathering designers, researchers, and product managers to explore how AI is reshaping UX and how to prepare strategies, tools, and workflows accordingly. Expect engaging keynotes from industry leaders, hands-on workshops, case studies, and a dedicated networking reception, all aimed at helping your team integrate AI into UX in meaningful, future-ready ways. If you’re looking to stay at the forefront of AI-powered UX design and research, this conference offers the insights, practical learning, and connections to make that happen. Link: https://condens.io/guides/ux-conference-guide-2026/
